summary: Three saved games! Level 1 after Helgen with the possibility to make a character just like you want to have it. The other two saved games are at level 10 and 20 (battlemage). See description and screenshots for more information about Mayra! Thanks for downloading! :)
descriptionHtml:
I recently started my third character, this time I saved my level 1 save for everyone (and myself *g*) who wants to try a new character. Mayra is level 20 now (saved game also uploaded), if you don\'t want to start from the beginning, maybe the level 10 or 20 - saves are the right ones for you!

[center][url=http://static.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/images/5903-1-1326244853.jpg][img]http://static.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/images/5903-1-1326244853.jpg[/img][/url][/center]

@Level 1 save:
- You just left Helgen and start directly in front of the cave. 

@Level 10 save (battlemage):
- Thane of Winterhold
- Whiterun just reached (Dragonsreach not visited, therefore no dragons killed, but 3 shouts learned)
- Started main quest at the college of Winterhold (done \"First lessons\" and \"Saarthal\", now at \"Hitting the books\")
- Done \"Shalidor\'s Insights\"
- Started Azura\'s quest
- Done Bleak Falls Barrow (without quest from Balgruuf)
- Found first Gauldur Amulet Fragment (Saarthal)
- Found 2 stones of Barenziah (Yngvild and Archmage\'s room)
- Found Arondil\'s diaries (needed later for a quest at the Thieves guild)
- Sven (bard) as compenion ^^ (you will probably search as soon as possible for a new follower :D)
- Mayra is wearing heavy armor + fighting with 1H (bound sword) and/or magical skills.
- Perks in: Heavy armor (25), Smithing (20), Enchanting (24), Destruction (27), Conjuration (41)
- As always I enlarged the carry weight a bit, using the console

@Level 20 (battlemage):
- Main quest next: \"The way of the voice\" (done 4/18)
- Main quest at the college of Winterhold next: \"Revealing the Unseen\" (5/10)
- Thane of Winterhold, Whiterun and Markath
- 2 Houses (Whiterun, Markath)
- Started at level 15 fighting dragons, 3 Souls, 3 Shouts
- Companions not visited yet
- Found four stones of Barenziah (Yngvild, Archmage\'s room, Dragonsreach, Fellglow Keep)
- Obtained Azura\'s Star
- Follower is Argis the Bulwark (Sven died ^^), Lydia should be somewhere around Dragonsreach
- Perks in: Heavy armor (34), Smithing (34), Enchanting (41), Destruction (43), Conjuration (59), Alteration (30),  Restoration (25). 
- No perks, but skilled: 1H (43)
- Standing stone: First 15 levels \"the Mage Stone\", since then \"The Lover Stone\" (learn all skills 15% faster)
- For more information see the screenshots

The screenshots are on German, but I think it should be no problem to understand/compare them with your game. The saved game should work with your game too!

=====================================================================================
If you like Mayra\'s look, you will need some mods to make her a beauty as on the screenshots:

- [url=http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=498]High quality eyes[/url]
- [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2812]Better females by Bella[/url]
- [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=4307]AOF believable hair[/url]
- [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=562]No helmet Mod[/url]

They are optional and not necessary for playing. Thanks for downloading and sorry for bad English. :) 

=====================================================================================

- [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=5342]Alexa (Highelf mage level 9 or 31)[/url]
